Fantasy Football\",\"Fantasy Football Analytics\",\"Draft Strategy\",\"Rankings\",\"Sports Product\",\"Data Products\",\"Next.js\"],\"articleSection\":\"Fantasy Football Analytics\",\"wordCount\":1201,\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com/writing/building-a-fantasy-football-rankings-platform\"}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"Building an Investment Research Platform That Prefers Clarity Over Spreadsheet Sprawl\",\"description\":\"An inside look at the investment research platform I built to combine curated company snapshots, valuation context, and browser-saved portfolio tracking in one calmer workflow.\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-04-02\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-04-02\",\"author\":{\"name\":\"Isaac Vazquez\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Isaac Vazquez\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com\"},\"mainEntityOfPage\":{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com/writing/building-an-investment-research-platform\"},\"keywords\":[\"Investment Research\",\"Fintech Product\",\"Portfolio Tracking\",\"Equity Analysis\",\"Financial Data\",\"Next.js\",\"Product Design\"],\"articleSection\":\"Fintech Product\",\"wordCount\":1299,\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com/writing/building-an-investment-research-platform\"}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"Building News Pulse: A Dashboard For Comparing How Major Outlets Cover The Same Story\",\"description\":\"How I built News Pulse, a media analytics dashboard that aggregates RSS feeds from major outlets, extracts lightweight topics and sentiment, and makes cross-outlet coverage easier to compare.\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-04-02\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-04-02\",\"author\":{\"name\":\"Isaac Vazquez\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Isaac Vazquez\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com\"},\"mainEntityOfPage\":{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com/writing/building-news-pulse-dashboard\"},\"keywords\":[\"Media Analytics\",\"News Product\",\"RSS\",\"Sentiment Analysis\",\"Topic Extraction\",\"Product Strategy\",\"Next.js\"],\"articleSection\":\"Media Analytics\",\"wordCount\":1095,\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com/writing/building-news-pulse-dashboard\"}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"Building SpaceX Mission Control: Turning Public Launch Data Into A Productized Mission Board\",\"description\":\"A look at how I built SpaceX Mission Control, a mission-board-style interface that turns public launch data into a deeper browsing experience with next-launch focus, deep links, and relationship-aware detail.\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-04-02\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-04-02\",\"author\":{\"name\":\"Isaac Vazquez\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Isaac Vazquez\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com\"},\"mainEntityOfPage\":{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com/writing/building-spacex-mission-control\"},\"keywords\":[\"Product Design\",\"Dashboard Design\",\"SpaceX\",\"API Design\",\"Data Product\",\"Next.js\",\"User Experience\"],\"articleSection\":\"Product Design\",\"wordCount\":1060,\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com/writing/building-spacex-mission-control\"}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"Interchange IQ: Building a Payment Fee Analyzer Around Real Processor Economics\",\"description\":\"Why I built Interchange IQ, a payments economics tool that compares flat-rate and interchange-plus pricing using published interchange data, card mix assumptions, and breakeven analysis.\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-04-02\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-04-02\",\"author\":{\"name\":\"Isaac Vazquez\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Isaac Vazquez\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com\"},\"mainEntityOfPage\":{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com/writing/interchange-iq-payment-fee-analyzer\"},\"keywords\":[\"Payments\",\"Interchange\",\"Fintech Product\",\"Pricing\",\"Processor Economics\",\"Product Strategy\",\"Next.js\"],\"articleSection\":\"Payments\",\"wordCount\":1147,\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com/writing/interchange-iq-payment-fee-analyzer\"}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"2026 March Madness Bracket Analysis: Best Upset Picks, Final Four, and Time Zone Traps\",\"description\":\"A full 2026 March Madness bracket breakdown with best upset picks, Final Four predictions, champion pick, and a closer look at the interactive model behind the time-zone travel penalties that create edges seed lines miss.\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-03-17\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-04-02\",\"author\":{\"name\":\"Isaac Vazquez\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Isaac Vazquez\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com\"},\"mainEntityOfPage\":{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com/writing/2026-march-madness-bracket-analysis\"},\"keywords\":[\"March Madness\",\"NCAA Tournament\",\"Sports Analytics\",\"Bracket Analysis\",\"KenPom\",\"Final Four\",\"Upset Picks\"],\"articleSection\":\"Sports Analytics\",\"wordCount\":1600,\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com/writing/2026-march-madness-bracket-analysis\"}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"2025 Fantasy Football Draft Strategy: Data-Driven Approach to Dominating Your League\",\"description\":\"Master your 2025 fantasy football draft with advanced analytics, tier-based strategies, and data-driven decision making. Learn how to leverage real-time data and algorithmic insights for draft dominance.\",\"datePublished\":\"2025-01-24\",\"dateModified\":\"2025-01-24\",\"author\":{\"name\":\"Isaac Vazquez\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Isaac Vazquez\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com\"},\"mainEntityOfPage\":{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com/writing/2025-fantasy-football-draft-strategy\"},\"keywords\":[\"Fantasy Football\",\"Draft Strategy\",\"Data Analytics\",\"NFL Draft\",\"Fantasy Draft\",\"Analytics Tools\",\"Draft Tiers\",\"Player Rankings\"],\"articleSection\":\"Fantasy Football Analytics\",\"wordCount\":2857,\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com/writing/2025-fantasy-football-draft-strategy\"}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"AI in Software Testing: The Future of Quality Assurance\",\"description\":\"Discover how artificial intelligence is revolutionizing software testing and quality assurance. From automated test generation to intelligent bug detection, explore the tools, techniques, and strategies that are transforming QA engineering in 2025 and beyond.\",\"datePublished\":\"2025-01-24\",\"dateModified\":\"2025-01-24\",\"author\":{\"name\":\"Isaac Vazquez\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Isaac Vazquez\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com\"},\"mainEntityOfPage\":{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com/writing/ai-in-software-testing-future-of-qa\"},\"keywords\":[\"AI\",\"Machine Learning\",\"Software Testing\",\"QA Engineering\",\"Test Automation\",\"Quality Assurance\",\"Artificial Intelligence\",\"Testing Strategy\",\"Innovation\",\"Future Tech\"],\"articleSection\"