d:text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">Building SpaceX Mission Control: Turning Public Launch Data Into A Productized Mission Board</h2><p class=\"text-base text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4 line-clamp-3 flex-grow\">A look at how I built SpaceX Mission Control, a mission-board-style interface that turns public launch data into a deeper browsing experience with next-launch focus, deep links, and relationship-aware detail.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-neutral-200 pt-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M4 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-12z\"></path><path d=\"M16 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M8 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M4 11h16\"></path><path d=\"M11 15h1\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v3\"></path></svg><time dateTime=\"2026-04-02\">Apr 1, 2026</time></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0a9 9 0 0 0 -18 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 7v5l3 3\"></path></svg><span>5 min read</span></div><div class=\"ml-auto\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3\"><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Product Design</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Dashboard Design</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->SpaceX</span></div></div></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/writing/interchange-iq-payment-fee-analyzer\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 flex h-full flex-col shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">Payments</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">Interchange IQ: Building a Payment Fee Analyzer Around Real Processor Economics</h2><p class=\"text-base text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4 line-clamp-3 flex-grow\">Why I built Interchange IQ, a payments economics tool that compares flat-rate and interchange-plus pricing using published interchange data, card mix assumptions, and breakeven analysis.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-neutral-200 pt-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M4 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-12z\"></path><path d=\"M16 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M8 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M4 11h16\"></path><path d=\"M11 15h1\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v3\"></path></svg><time dateTime=\"2026-04-02\">Apr 1, 2026</time></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0a9 9 0 0 0 -18 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 7v5l3 3\"></path></svg><span>6 min read</span></div><div class=\"ml-auto\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3\"><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Payments</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Interchange</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Fintech Product</span></div></div></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/writing/2026-march-madness-bracket-analysis\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 flex h-full flex-col shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">Sports Analytics</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">2026 March Madness Bracket Analysis: Best Upset Picks, Final Four, and Time Zone Traps</h2><p class=\"text-base text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4 line-clamp-3 flex-grow\">A full 2026 March Madness bracket breakdown with best upset picks, Final Four predictions, champion pick, and a closer look at the interactive model behind the time-zone travel penalties that create edges seed lines miss.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-neutral-200 pt-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M4 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-12z\"></path><path d=\"M16 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M8 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M4 11h16\"></path><path d=\"M11 15h1\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v3\"></path></svg><time dateTime=\"2026-03-17\">Mar 16, 2026</time></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0a9 9 0 0 0 -18 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 7v5l3 3\"></path></svg><span>7 min read</span></div><div class=\"ml-auto\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3\"><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->March Madness</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->NCAA Tournament</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Sports Analytics</span></div></div></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/writing/2025-fantasy-football-draft-strategy\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 flex h-full flex-col shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">Fantasy Football Analytics</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">2025 Fantasy Football Draft Strategy: Data-Driven Approach to Dominating Your League</h2><p class=\"text-base text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4 line-clamp-3 flex-grow\">Master your 2025 fantasy football draft with advanced analytics, tier-based strategies, and data-driven decision making. Learn how to leverage real-time data and algorithmic insights for draft dominance.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-neutral-200 pt-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M4 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-12z\"></path><path d=\"M16 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M8 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M4 11h16\"></path><path d=\"M11 15h1\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v3\"></path></svg><time dateTime=\"2025-01-24\">Jan 23, 2025</time></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0a9 9 0 0 0 -18 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 7v5l3 3\"></path></svg><span>10 min read</span></div><div class=\"ml-auto\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3\"><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Fantasy Football</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Draft Strategy</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Data Analytics</span></div></div></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/writing/ai-in-software-testing-future-of-qa\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 flex h-full flex-col shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">QA Engineering</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">AI in Software Testing: The Future of Quality Assurance</h2><p class=\"text-base text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4 line-clamp-3 flex-grow\">Discover how artificial intelligence is revolutionizing software testing and quality assurance. From automated test generation to intelligent bug detection, explore the tools, techniques, and strategies that are transforming QA engineering in 2025 and beyond.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-neutral-200 pt-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M4 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-12z\"></path><path d=\"M16 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M8 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M4 11h16\"></path><path d=\"M11 15h1\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v3\"></path></svg><time dateTime=\"2025-01-24\">Jan 23, 2025</time></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0a9 9 0 0 0 -18 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 7v5l3 3\"></path></svg><span>21 min read</span></div><div class=\"ml-auto\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3\"><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->AI</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Machine Learning</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Software Testing</span></div></div></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/writing/building-ai-powered-analytics-fantasy-football-to-enterprise\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 flex h-full flex-col shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">AI &amp; Analytics</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">Building AI-Powered Analytics: Lessons from Fantasy Football to Enterprise</h2><p class=\"text-base text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4 line-clamp-3 flex-grow\">Learn how to build production-ready AI analytics systems by exploring real-world implementation patterns. From fantasy football analytics to enterprise solutions, discover the architecture decisions, data pipelines, and scaling strategies that power modern AI-driven applications.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-neutral-200 pt-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M4 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-12z\"></path><path d=\"M16 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M8 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M4 11h16\"></path><path d=\"M11 15h1\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v3\"></path></svg><time dateTime=\"2025-01-24\">Jan 23, 2025</time></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0a9 9 0 0 0 -18 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 7v5l3 3\"></path></svg><span>19 min read</span></div><div class=\"ml-auto\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3\"><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->AI</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Analytics</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Machine Learning</span></div></div></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/writing/building-reliable-software-systems\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 flex h-full flex-col shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">Software Quality</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">Building Reliable Software Systems: A Complete Guide to Software Quality</h2><p class=\"text-base text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4 line-clamp-3 flex-grow\">Master the art of building reliable, maintainable software systems from Austin civic tech to Silicon Valley scale. This comprehensive guide combines technical excellence with strategic business thinking, covering quality principles, architecture patterns, and best practices from both emerging and mature tech markets.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-neutral-200 pt-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M4 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-12z\"></path><path d=\"M16 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M8 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M4 11h16\"></path><path d=\"M11 15h1\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v3\"></path></svg><time dateTime=\"2025-01-24\">Jan 23, 2025</time></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0a9 9 0 0 0 -18 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 7v5l3 3\"></path></svg><span>42 min read</span></div><div class=\"ml-auto\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3\"><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Software Quality</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->System Architecture</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Testing</span></div></div></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/writing/complete-guide-qa-engineering\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 flex h-full flex-col shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">QA Engineering</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">The Complete Guide to QA Engineering: Building Quality into Software Development</h2><p class=\"text-base text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4 line-clamp-3 flex-grow\">A comprehensive deep-dive into QA engineering practices, testing strategies, and quality assurance methodologies from both Austin and Bay Area perspectives. Learn how to build robust software systems with confidence through systematic testing approaches, strategic business thinking, and modern QA techniques that drive business value.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-neutral-200 pt-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M4 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-12z\"></path><path d=\"M16 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M8 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M4 11h16\"></path><path d=\"M11 15h1\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v3\"></path></svg><time dateTime=\"2025-01-24\">Jan 23, 2025</time></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0a9 9 0 0 0 -18 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 7v5l3 3\"></path></svg><span>22 min read</span></div><div class=\"ml-auto\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3\"><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->QA Engineering</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Software Testing</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Quality Assurance</span></div></div></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/writing/cybersecurity-in-age-of-ai-software-engineer-perspective\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 flex h-full flex-col shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">Cybersecurity</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">Cybersecurity in the Age of AI: A Software Engineer&#x27;s Perspective</h2><p class=\"text-base text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4 line-clamp-3 flex-grow\">Explore how artificial intelligence is transforming both cybersecurity threats and defenses. Learn about AI-powered attacks, intelligent security systems, and the critical considerations every software engineer must understand to build secure, AI-aware applications in 2025 and beyond.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-neutral-200 pt-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M4 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-12z\"></path><path d=\"M16 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M8 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M4 11h16\"></path><path d=\"M11 15h1\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v3\"></path></svg><time dateTime=\"2025-01-24\">Jan 23, 2025</time></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0a9 9 0 0 0 -18 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 7v5l3 3\"></path></svg><span>22 min read</span></div><div class=\"ml-auto\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3\"><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Cybersecurity</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Artificial Intelligence</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Software Security</span></div></div></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/writing/evolution-software-architecture-monoliths-ai-native-systems\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 flex h-full flex-col shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">Software Architecture</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">The Evolution of Software Architecture: From Monoliths to AI-Native Systems</h2><p class=\"text-base text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4 line-clamp-3 flex-grow\">Trace the architectural journey from monolithic applications to AI-native systems, exploring how business strategy, technical constraints, and emerging technologies have shaped software design. Learn to architect systems that can evolve with AI integration while maintaining reliability and performance at scale.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-neutral-200 pt-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M4 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-12z\"></path><path d=\"M16 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M8 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M4 11h16\"></path><path d=\"M11 15h1\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v3\"></path></svg><time dateTime=\"2025-01-24\">Jan 23, 2025</time></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0a9 9 0 0 0 -18 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 7v5l3 3\"></path></svg><span>34 min read</span></div><div class=\"ml-auto\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3\"><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Software Architecture</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->System Design</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Microservices</span></div></div></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/writing/fantasy-football-beginners-complete-guide\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 flex h-full flex-col shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">Fantasy Football Analytics</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">Fantasy Football for Beginners: Your Complete 2025 Starter Guide</h2><p class=\"text-base text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4 line-clamp-3 flex-grow\">New to fantasy football? This comprehensive beginner&#x27;s guide covers everything you need to know to start playing and competing in 2025. Learn the basics, essential strategies, and how to avoid common mistakes.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-neutral-200 pt-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M4 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-12z\"></path><path d=\"M16 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M8 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M4 11h16\"></path><path d=\"M11 15h1\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v3\"></path></svg><time dateTime=\"2025-01-24\">Jan 23, 2025</time></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0a9 9 0 0 0 -18 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 7v5l3 3\"></path></svg><span>19 min read</span></div><div class=\"ml-auto\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3\"><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Fantasy Football</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Beginners Guide</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Getting Started</span></div></div></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/writing/getting-started-with-automated-testing\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 flex h-full flex-col shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">QA Engineering</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">Getting Started with Automated Testing: A QA Engineer&#x27;s Strategic Guide</h2><p class=\"text-base text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4 line-clamp-3 flex-grow\">Learn the fundamentals of automated testing from both technical and business perspectives. This comprehensive guide covers testing strategies, frameworks, and best practices for building reliable test suites that drive business value across Austin and Bay Area tech markets.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-neutral-200 pt-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M4 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-12z\"></path><path d=\"M16 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M8 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M4 11h16\"></path><path d=\"M11 15h1\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v3\"></path></svg><time dateTime=\"2025-01-24\">Jan 23, 2025</time></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0a9 9 0 0 0 -18 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 7v5l3 3\"></path></svg><span>5 min read</span></div><div class=\"ml-auto\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3\"><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Testing</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Automation</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->QA</span></div></div></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/writing/low-code-no-code-vs-traditional-development-when-to-choose\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 flex h-full flex-col shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">Software Development</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">Low-Code/No-Code vs Traditional Development: When to Choose What</h2><p class=\"text-base text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4 line-clamp-3 flex-grow\">Navigate the evolving landscape of software development approaches with strategic insights from both Austin&#x27;s collaborative tech culture and Silicon Valley&#x27;s innovation ecosystem. Learn when to leverage low-code/no-code platforms versus traditional development, and how to build hybrid solutions that maximize business value.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-neutral-200 pt-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M4 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-12z\"></path><path d=\"M16 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M8 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M4 11h16\"></path><path d=\"M11 15h1\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v3\"></path></svg><time dateTime=\"2025-01-24\">Jan 23, 2025</time></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0a9 9 0 0 0 -18 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 7v5l3 3\"></path></svg><span>29 min read</span></div><div class=\"ml-auto\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3\"><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Low-Code</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->No-Code</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Traditional Development</span></div></div></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/writing/mastering-fantasy-football-analytics\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 flex h-full flex-col shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">Fantasy Football Analytics</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">Mastering Fantasy Football Analytics: A Data-Driven Approach to Winning</h2><p class=\"text-base text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4 line-clamp-3 flex-grow\">Dive deep into fantasy football analytics with advanced data visualization, algorithmic strategies, and machine learning techniques. Learn how to build sophisticated tools and gain competitive advantages through data science.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-neutral-200 pt-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M4 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-12z\"></path><path d=\"M16 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M8 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M4 11h16\"></path><path d=\"M11 15h1\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v3\"></path></svg><time dateTime=\"2025-01-24\">Jan 23, 2025</time></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0a9 9 0 0 0 -18 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 7v5l3 3\"></path></svg><span>41 min read</span></div><div class=\"ml-auto\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3\"><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Fantasy Football</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Data Analytics</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Data Visualization</span></div></div></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/writing/qa-engineer-guide-testing-ai-systems\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 flex h-full flex-col shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">QA Engineering</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">The QA Engineer&#x27;s Guide to Testing AI Systems: Quality Assurance for Machine Learning</h2><p class=\"text-base text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4 line-clamp-3 flex-grow\">Navigate the unique challenges of testing AI and machine learning systems with proven QA methodologies. From model validation to bias detection, learn comprehensive testing strategies that ensure your AI applications are reliable, fair, and production-ready.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-neutral-200 pt-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M4 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-12z\"></path><path d=\"M16 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M8 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M4 11h16\"></path><path d=\"M11 15h1\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v3\"></path></svg><time dateTime=\"2025-01-24\">Jan 23, 2025</time></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0a9 9 0 0 0 -18 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 7v5l3 3\"></path></svg><span>19 min read</span></div><div class=\"ml-auto\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3\"><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->AI Testing</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->Machine Learning</span><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">#<!-- -->QA Engineering</span></div></div></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/writing/qa-engineering-silicon-valley-uc-berkeley-mba-perspective\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 flex h-full flex-col shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">QA Engineering</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">QA Engineering in Silicon Valley: Insights from a UC Berkeley MBA Perspective</h2><p class=\"text-base text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4 line-clamp-3 flex-grow\">Explore how Silicon Valley&#x27;s innovation culture shapes quality assurance practices, combining technical QA expertise with strategic business thinking from UC Berkeley Haas School of Business. Learn about the unique challenges and opportunities for QA engineers in the Bay Area tech ecosystem.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-neutral-200 pt-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http:/